     1‚Üí# mdbook-compare
     3‚ÜíThis is a simple utility to compare the output of two different versions of mdbook.
     4‚Üí
     5‚ÜíTo use this:
     6‚Üí
     7‚Üí1. Install [`tidy`](https://www.html-tidy.org/).
     8‚Üí2. Install or build the initial version of mdbook that you want to compare.
     9‚Üí3. Install or build the new version of mdbook that you want to compare.
    10‚Üí4. Run `mdbook-compare` with the arguments to the mdbook executables and the books to build.
